HEADWORD: Unequity
<hw>Un*eq"ui*ty</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Want of equity or
uprightness; injustice; wickedness; iniquity.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
